    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one and it seriously looks and drives like it\u2019s brand new! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next big adventure, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
