    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an unparalleled driving experience, this E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example is a purist\u2019s specification with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated M-Variable differential lock. The mechanical integrity is beyond reproach: the subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing across the power band. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a meticulously maintained suspension featuring refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers to preserve the iconic 50/50 weight distribution. Cosmetically, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster wear, signifying a true concours-level survivor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
