      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for your dream ride? You've found it! This car is honestly in breathtaking condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've absolutely babied this beauty, keeping it garage-parked and sparkling clean. It drives like a total dream and is ready for a new adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
